    "question_id" : 21746136,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>As explained <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/6018701/how-is-mvn-clean-install-different-from-mvn-install\">here</a>.</p>\n\n<p>clean is its own action in Maven. mvn clean install tell Maven to do the clean action in each module before running the install action for each module.</p>\n\n<p>What this does is clear any compiled files you have, making sure that you're really compiling each module from scratch.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "comments" : [ {
      "owner" : {
        "account_id" : 1937747,
        "reputation" : 15080,
